<br>
1. A volunteer will create a thread called &quot;Level 1 Spells&quot; (I will need a volunteer for every spell level).<br>
2. That original thread will list every spell available for that level.<br>
3. That volunteer (original poster) will be responsible for editing his original post with the information threaded below it that other viewers add.<br>
4. The info needed is:<br>
    City found in, building found in, Vendor name (if applicable)<br>
    Approximate cost sold for (if applicable)<br>
    Zone found in, Mob dropped from (if applicable)<br>
    Research runes needed (if applicable)<br>
<br>
